==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nonuniformist
<hw>Non*u"ni*form`ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
believes that past changes in the structure of the earth have proceeded
from cataclysms or causes more violent than are now operating; -- called
also <altname>nonuniformitarian</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nonunion</ent>⟦br⟧
